dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Washburn County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2019. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Washburn_Hydro_2019.gdb'. The features layers included in this geodatabase are 'Washburn_Hydro_2019_Line' and 'Washburn_Hydro_2019_Poly'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
